    "The success of Scenario 4 can be attributed to its unique approach, which combines hybrid TL and relevance to a specific domain, which leads to a high level of generalisation with a better representation of the features.",
    "Moreover, its performance is further enhanced by the feature fusion technique employed.",
    "This combination enables the model to leverage preexisting knowledge while adapting specifically to the target dataset.",
    "As a result, it performs better in detecting abnormalities in shoulder X-ray images.",
    "Part 2: Experimental assessment of deep-feature fusion Several ML classifiers have been trained and tested with extracted features from seven models, including Decision Tree, Linear Discriminant, Naive Bayes, SVMs, K-Nearest Neighbour, Logistic Regression, and Neural Networks."
